Spring is the most popular Java framework for building enterprise applications.

**Core concepts:**
- **IoC Container** — manages object lifecycle and wiring
- **Beans** — objects managed by Spring
- **Dependency Injection** — Spring injects dependencies automatically

```java
@Component
public class GreetService {
    public String greet(String name) { return "Hello, " + name; }
}

@RestController
public class GreetController {
    @Autowired
    private GreetService greetService;

    @GetMapping("/greet/{name}")
    public String greet(@PathVariable String name) {
        return greetService.greet(name);
    }
}
```
